HEADWORD: Mara
<hw>Ma"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr.
<ets>m⟦amac⟧ra</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Hind. Myth.)</fld> <def>The principal
or ruling evil spirit.</def> <rj><au>E. Arnold.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mara</ent>⟦br⟧
